
'''= Collaborative housing projects in Catalonia''' 

URL = http://commoninghousing.net/cophab-map/

=Description=

"Collaborative housing projects in Catalonia are moving from construction or refurbishment to inhabitation. We have just updated our COPHAB map with updates about projects that will start inhabitation before the end of 2018. There are now 16 (168 dwellings in total) which are inhabited or about to be: 11 of them were set up since 2011, showing rapid and exponential growth."

=More information=

'[[Commoning Housing]]' aims to analyse contextual and specific possibilities and barriers to practices of housing 'commoning' beyond traditional forms of state and market provision, to identify and share translocal theoretical and methodological lessons through case studies in Barcelona and London. For more information, see: http://commoninghousing.net/


